'howToPlayDialog.pages.text3': ['Letters Bank:\nThe game is played with a bank of letters, including 2 Jokers that\ncan be used in place of any letter.\nThe letters are randomly selected from the bank, and only used once.\nEach round begins with a fresh bank of letters.'],
