'howToPlayDialog.pages.text5': ["To return a selected letter from the board, move the cursor to the letter and press\nSELECT key.\nReplacing Letters: Replace a selected letter with another letter from\nthe bank by choosing and pressing the 'REPLACE LETTER' button."],
'howToPlayDialog.pages.text6': ["Submitting a Word:\nUse the 'SUBMIT WORD' button after forming a word on the board.\nOnly words of two or more letters are permitted.\nProper nouns, like the names of people and places, are not permitted."],
'howToPlayDialog.pages.text7': ['Basic Scoring:\nPoints for each word are awarded as follows:'],
