'howToPlayDialog.pages.text14': ['Triples the score of the letter placed on it.'],
'howToPlayDialog.pages.text16': ['Doubles the score of the word placed on it.'],
'howToPlayDialog.pages.text18': ['Triples the score of the word placed on it. This is the most powerful\nbonus.'],
'howToPlayDialog.pages.text20': ['Doubles the score of the letter placed on it and adds seconds to the\ntimer.'],
'howToPlayDialog.pages.text22': ['Triples the score of the letter placed on it and adds seconds to the timer.'],
'howToPlayDialog.pages.text23': ['3. Bingo Bonus:  100 bonus points, along with a golden sensei icon,'],
'howToPlayDialog.pages.text24': ['are awarded for playing a seven letter word.\nFive golden sensei icons in a round initiate a Bingo Round.'],
'howToPlayDialog.pages.text25': ['4. Bingo Round: 100 points are awarded for forming a single seven letter word'],
'howToPlayDialog.pages.text26': ['in a limited amount of time without exchanging any letters.'],
'howToPlayDialog.pages.text27': ['Total Score:\nThe Total Score is calculated at the end of each complete round.'],
'howToPlayDialog.pages.text28': ['1. Words bonus: Five points are awarded for each word played.'],
'howToPlayDialog.pages.text29': ['2. Time Bonus: Two points are awarded for every second remaining on the timer.'],
'howToPlayDialog.pages.text30': ['3. Letter Bonus: Two points are awarded for each unplayed letter left on screen'],
'howToPlayDialog.pages.text31': ['and in the bank.'],
'howToPlayDialog.pages.text32': ['4. Target Bonus: The number of points by which the total score exceeds'],
